---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="API Pricing for SaaS - Use Case | SaaS Pricing Toolkit"
  description="A simple flow for pricing an API product: estimate costs, back into target margin, and compare seat vs usage."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Use case: API pricing for SaaS</h1>
    <p>
      This flow helps you turn your call volume and unit costs into a recommended monthly price and an implied rate per
      1,000 calls.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a class="btn primary" href="/saas-pricing/api-pricing-calculator/">Start with API pricing</a>
      <a class="btn ghost" href="/saas-pricing/">Back to toolkit</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grid">
    <section class="card col8">
      <h2>Recommended steps</h2>
      <ol class="list">
        <li>
          Estimate a plan price from calls and costs: <a href="/saas-pricing/api-pricing-calculator/">API pricing calculator</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          Cross-check your unit pricing model:{" "}
          <a href="/saas-pricing/usage-based-pricing-calculator/">usage-based pricing calculator</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          Compare to a seat plan for the same customer:{" "}
          <a href="/saas-pricing/seat-vs-usage-pricing-comparison/">seat vs usage pricing comparison</a>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">Notes</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Enter your blended infra cost per 1,000 calls (compute + DB + vendor + observability).</li>
        <li>Use monthly fixed cost for support, tooling, and baseline overhead.</li>
        <li>Export CSV to document assumptions for internal review.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <aside class="card col4">
      <h2>Shortcut</h2>
      <p class="muted">If your pricing is primarily usage-based, start with unit pricing first.</p>
      <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
        <a class="btn" href="/saas-pricing/usage-based-pricing-calculator/">Unit pricing</a>
      </div>
      <div class="ad" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Ad slot (optional)</div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

